{"tid":2214511,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"科學家警告神經疾病患者或於疫情後大增","createTime":"2020-09-23T10:01:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T10:13:37.000Z","uid":239336,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"901f591ce9978da787be55d79806a7beb5c3f3b2","tid":2214511,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T10:01:00.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】新冠病毒疫情爆發以來，患者除了會出現發燒、咳嗽等表徵外，病毒還會攻擊人體多個器官，包括對大腦和中樞神經系統造成損害。有科學家擔心可能會引發嚴重後果。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲廣播公司報道，澳洲有研究團隊發現，新冠病毒長遠可能會導致病人患上神經系統疾病，警告患柏金遜症等疾病的人數在疫情過後可能會大增，甚至出現爆炸性增長。<br />\n<br />\n大約一百年前，西班牙爆發流感大流行，在事後的五年，柏金遜症的發病率大增三倍。科學家警告新冠病毒可能引發類似的疾病潮。<br />\n<br />\n專家指，柏金遜症這種神經系統疾病是一種複雜的疾病，其中一個成因是腦炎，而新冠病毒正正可以引發腦部發炎，腦部一旦發炎，就可以引致連串反應，最終可能導致柏金遜症。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=406589\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406589&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9qooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=6d260e17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D406589&h=5be6b1ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/international/player?newsId=406589</a><br />\n<br />\n啲中過招既黑警小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd5e5959c542c906b677d193fbf60dee460a316","tid":2214511,"uid":239336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T10:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cb36308fa3e40be877798d0a79b51ee19c4dd8","tid":2214511,"uid":126648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T10:13:37.000Z","msg":"恐懼撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}